Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:48.04,POS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)\pos(640,540)\be2}贝莉内特宅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐  请您一路小心
